OL,3,CHow Merlin the duck became Mexico's
OL,4,Cviral World Cup 'ambassador'
OL,6,FMeet Merlin - a pet duck turned
OL,7,Funofficial World Cup mascot for Mexico.
OL,9,FAfter Mexico's 2-0 victory over South
OL,10,FAfrica, Merlin waddled along with fans
OL,11,Fparading through Mexico City, wearing
OL,12,Fthe national team jersey and custom
OL,13,Fsocks.
OL,15,FUnsurprisingly, footage of Merlin the
OL,16,Fduck quickly went viral, racking up
OL,17,Fmillions of views on social media.
OL,19,FMerlin the duck has stolen the hearts
OL,20,Fof fans in Mexico City
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
