OL,3,CHow Merlin the duck became Mexico's
OL,4,Cviral World Cup 'ambassador'
OL,6,FPeople across the world were instantly
OL,7,Fcaptivated by his charm, with one
OL,8,Fperson online declaring "This duck is
OL,9,Falready a national treasure".
OL,11,FAnother said Merlin was "the best
OL,12,Fthing about the World Cup so far," and
OL,13,Fothers called for Merlin to join the
OL,14,Fteam in the stadium.
OL,16,FIn Mexico City, however, Merlin was
OL,17,Falready something of a local celebrity.
