CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781910185
OL,3,CHow Merlin the duck became Mexico's
OL,4,Cviral World Cup 'ambassador'
OL,6,FThe duck regularly accompanies his
OL,7,Fowner, Carla Gomez, who sells water
OL,8,Fand soft drinks from a little cart
OL,9,Feach weekend.
OL,11,F"We don't like to leave him alone at
OL,12,Fhome; we like him to be with us. He's
OL,13,Four baby," Gomez said.
OL,15,FRain or shine, Merlin follows Gomez
OL,16,Fand her son Cristian through some of
OL,17,Fthe capital's best-known landmarks,
OL,18,Fincluding Alameda Central, the Palace
OL,19,Fof Fine Arts and the Zocalo square.
