PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781910185
OL,3,CHow Merlin the duck became Mexico's
OL,4,Cviral World Cup 'ambassador'
OL,6,F"He is always with us when we're out
OL,7,Fselling," said Gomez "We never
OL,8,Fimagined it would take off like that,
OL,9,Fbut we're really happy about it... We
OL,10,Fweren't expecting it."
OL,12,FNow, the family hopes Mexico's most
OL,13,Ffamous feathered supporter can
OL,14,Fcontinue bringing luck to the team,
OL,15,Fwho are already through to the
OL,16,Fknockout stages.
OL,18,F"Mexico, we are with you," Gomez said.
OL,19,F"And Merlin is your number one fan."
